Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Safety or pip-audit not found

Solution: Ensure virtual environment is activated: source venv/bin/activate
Issue: Tests fail to import app module

Solution: Check PYTHONPATH or run tests from project root
Issue: npm audit shows vulnerabilities

Solution: Run npm audit fix for automatic fixes, review breaking changes first
Issue: Permission denied on scripts

Solution: Run chmod +x script_name.sh to make executable
